  "text": "However, in their review, Grunert and Wills highlighted that even if consumers appreciate simplification, they would like to know what the simplified information reflects [CITATION_1] , which could explain why Tick was the least preferred label.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "37925758"
